descript.abstract: Various private, state, and federal entities have entered into agreements with or sold lands to IDFG for the management of the state's fish and wildlife. Each property agreement/lease/deed/easement/permit in Bob Martin's (IDFG) Lands database was mapped based on their legal descriptions. This dataset depicts those lands that make up IDFG's wildlife managment areas (WMAs). Various layers were used to help digitize each area: township range section, geographic names, ITD roads, FS roads, hydrography, land ownership, county boundaries, etc. This shapefile was created by combining the mapping efforts of Pamela Bond and Angie Schmidt of IDFG and the Idaho Department of Lands. Much of the lands owned by IDFG or leased from IDL can be searched for viewed on the IDL website: http://gis1.idl.idaho.gov.
